ich is done through a team of documentation officers at head office as well as branch office.  Responsible for the implementation and monitoring of statutory compliance of the organization centrally at head office, viz. Employee Provident Fund (EPF), ESIC, Workmen compensation policies, Medical insurance, Group personnel accident policies & their renewal process.  Responsible for Full & Final settlement of Exiting employees by developing smooth exit clearance and exit interview process, thus making people comfortable even at the time of exit from the organization. Also completion of the Gratuity process in case of long associated employees. ADDITIONAL FUNCTION’S PORTFOLIOS Handling international shipment & logistic related all activity from India to UAE, OMAN for project materials shipment purpose as per our company project requirement. ACHIEVEMENT: Two Consecutive Years (2012-2013) awarded as “Best Performance – Accounts & Administration” in M/S IOT Anwesha Engineering & Construction Ltd. | MIS | 2019-2019"}]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, 'F:\Resume All 1\Resume PDF\Ashis Karfa.pdf', 'Name: Administration Professional

